# Video - KX Dashboards

Original URL: https://code.kx.com/dashboards/video/

# Video

![Screenshot](../img/video/videcontent.jpg)

A container for video content.

## Set up

  1. Define the location of the .mp4 file in _Video Source_.

  2. If the video is to play on dashboard load, set _Playing_ to `0`.

## Settings

![Screenshot](../img/video/videosettings.png)

_Name_

    A name for the component provided by the user. 
_BaseTime_

    Date and time of first video frame.
_Position_

    A `timestamp` of the current video frame mapped to a [view state parameter](../viewstateparameters/).
_Playing_

    Define for playback: `0` is static, `1` plays forward, `-1` plays backwards. Multiples, e.g. `4` will play at x4 speed.
_Video Source_

    URL for video .mp4 file.

## Style, Margins, Format

[Style](../style/#component-style) for common settings

